---
title: Cal Smart Shrimp and Bulgur Bowls with Tangy Herb Aioli and Roasted Veggies
description: Slightly smoky, herby and chock full of veggies, this calorie smart meal has it all! Pan-seared shrimp sit over a bulgur, roasted veggies and baby spinach. Zingy chimichurri-inspired aioli drizzle brings the entire dish together in a snap!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-crevettes-et-de-boulgour-2ab0b663.jpg
